## 10. Responsive Design Breakpoints

```css
/* Mobile first approach */
sm: 640px   /* Small tablets */
md: 768px   /* Tablets */
lg: 1024px  /* Laptops */
xl: 1280px  /* Desktops */
2xl: 1400px /* Large screens */
```

**Layout Behavior**:
- Mobile (<768px): Single column, stacked layout, sticky action bar
- Tablet (768-1024px): Two column with narrower clothing section
- Desktop (>1024px): Full two-column layout with generous spacing

